::Shredder::

One of Shredder's eyebrow's raise at Quickstrike's comments.

"Stop dragging you around?" he says in an amused tone, "I dragged you out of 
a very dangerous situation back there, and I get no thanks."

He laughs, standing up and turning around. "I do suggest you get to a CR 
chamber before you get in trouble again," he says, walking off.
